##
## Mirrorlist for the FactoriOS live env and the installer's pacstrap.
##
## A small set of globally-reliable tier-1 / CDN mirrors. The installer
## inherits this file (pacstrap reads the live env's pacman config) but
## does *not* copy it to the installed system — pacstrap drops the stock
## pacman-mirrorlist package on /mnt with everything commented out, so a
## post-install reflector run is the right way to set things up for
## updates on an installed FactoriOS.
##

## Cloudflare global CDN
Server = https://cloudflaremirrors.com/archlinux/$repo/os/$arch

## Official geographic anycast mirror
Server = https://geo.mirror.pkgbuild.com/$repo/os/$arch

## Rackspace, globally reliable
Server = https://mirror.rackspace.com/archlinux/$repo/os/$arch
